descriptionHtml:
Images - left one is after, right one is before.

Retexture of fishes in the game (standard size).
There is not salmon retexture, only the \'unable to touch\' fishes. They are retextured only so they look more exotic and fantasy-like. You might want this, if you are fantasy-gourmet.
And please understand, this is my first mod and I\'m not in that good at all, I recommend a backup if you do not like it.

Place into: data\\textures\\critters\\fish
I\'ll also continue with retexturing (can\'t call this modding) And i have alot of things to learn about.
Added 1.01 (better eye+coloring)
Report bugs (there should be no one)

I also guess, that i will continue retexturing the fishes to bigger sized texture (8192x8192/4096x4096)... we\'ll see.

Other work (you might also want from my collection):
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4684]Dogs ReTexture[/url] - COMPLETED 27.12.2011

If you like it (i hope you do), endorse me! 
Thanks for support.
